overview: "Which of the problems I raised will be adopted?" "Who will solve my problems and how?" This time, following the previous work, we will ask you to answer "worries" from the members and staff who arrived at the fictitious radio program "Oh! 7.83 THE CLEAR" sometimes seriously and sometimes roughly. Disc 1 (86mins), Disc 2 (85mins).
title: Hello! Project DVD Magazine Vol.74
